(103, 1, '2018-11-20 08:41:39', '2018-11-20 01:41:39', 'Chuỗi siêu thị American Home Depot ngày càng được mở rộng với mục tiêu đến gần hơn với người tiêu dùng.\r\nNgày 24/01/2018 vừa qua, Công ty American Home Việt Nam đã khai trương siêu thị VLXD - NT American Home Depot Ánh Dương Furniture tại Xã Vĩnh Lộc B, Bình Chánh, TP.HCM - cửa ngõ phía tây của TP.HCM, và là vị trí chiến lược đầy tiềm năng phát triển sôi động.\r\nKhách hàng có thể lựa chọn đầy đủ, hiệu quả và tin cậy với tiêu chí hoạt động CHÍNH HÃNG - CHẤT LƯỢNG - GIÁ RẺ.\r\nCùng xem lại một số hình ảnh tại buổi lễ khai trương:\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://bichngoan.local/khai-truong-sieu-thi-vlxd-nt-american-home-depot-anh-duong-furniture-tp-ho-chi-minh.html/dsc05943\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-104\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-104\" src=\"http://bichngoan.local/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/DSC05943.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /></a> <a href=\"http://bichngoan.local/khai-truong-sieu-thi-vlxd-nt-american-home-depot-anh-duong-furniture-tp-ho-chi-minh.html/dsc05948\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-105\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-105\" src=\"http://bichngoan.local/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/DSC05948.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"480\" /></a> <a href=\"http://bichngoan.local/khai-truong-sieu-thi-vlxd-nt-american-home-depot-anh-duong-furniture-tp-ho-chi-minh.html/dsc05959\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-106\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-106\" src=\"http://bichngoan.local/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/DSC05959.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /></a> <a href=\"http://bichngoan.local/khai-truong-sieu-thi-vlxd-nt-american-home-depot-anh-duong-furniture-tp-ho-chi-minh.html/dsc05969\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-107\"><img class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-107\" src=\"http://bichngoan.local/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/DSC05969.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"640\" height=\"426\" /></a> <a href=\"http